datasets.name: ae01d001
queryLines:
WITH workspace AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name,
    concat(COALESCE(workspace_name, ''), ' (id: ', workspace_id, ')') AS workspace_label
  FROM access.workspaces_latest
),
workspace_filtered AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name, workspace_label
  FROM workspace
  WHERE IF(:param_workspace = '<ALL WORKSPACES>', TRUE, workspace_label = :param_workspace)
),
audit_users AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT
    user_identity.email AS user_email,
    CASE WHEN user_identity.email LIKE '%@%' THEN 'Human' ELSE 'Service Principal' END AS user_type
  FROM access.audit a
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON a.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE a.event_date BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
),
query_count AS (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS cnt
  FROM query.history q
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON q.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE CAST(q.start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
),
job_count AS (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS cnt
  FROM lakeflow.job_run_timeline j
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON j.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE CAST(j.period_start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
),
dbu_total AS (
  SELECT ROUND(SUM(usage_quantity), 1) AS cnt
  FROM billing.usage u
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON u.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE u.usage_date BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
)
SELECT
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM audit_users WHERE user_type = 'Human') AS active_users,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM audit_users WHERE user_type = 'Service Principal') AS service_principals,
  (SELECT cnt FROM query_count) AS total_queries,
  (SELECT cnt FROM job_count) AS total_job_runs,
  (SELECT cnt FROM dbu_total) AS total_dbus,
  ROUND(CAST((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM audit_users WHERE user_type = 'Human') AS DOUBLE) /
    NULLIF((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM audit_users WHERE user_type = 'Service Principal'), 0), 1) AS user_sp_ratio

datasets.name: ae01d002
queryLines:

    concat(COALESCE(workspace_name, ''), ' (id: ', workspace_id, ')') AS workspace_label

workspace_filtered AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name, workspace_label
  FROM workspace

)
SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN :param_time_key = 'Month' THEN date_trunc('MONTH', a.event_date)
    WHEN :param_time_key = 'Week' THEN date_trunc('WEEK', a.event_date)
    ELSE a.event_date
  END AS time_key,
  CASE WHEN user_identity.email LIKE '%@%' THEN 'Human' ELSE 'Service Principal' END AS user_type,
  COUNT(DISTINCT user_identity.email) AS distinct_users
FROM access.audit a
INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON a.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
WHERE a.event_date BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
GROUP BY time_key, user_type
ORDER BY time_key

datasets.name: ae01d012
queryLines:
WITH workspace AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name,
    concat(COALESCE(workspace_name, ''), ' (id: ', workspace_id, ')') AS workspace_label
  FROM access.workspaces_latest
),
workspace_filtered AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name, workspace_label
  FROM workspace
  WHERE IF(:param_workspace = '<ALL WORKSPACES>', TRUE, workspace_label = :param_workspace)
),
weekly_stats AS (
  SELECT
    date_trunc('WEEK', a.event_date) AS week_start,
    COUNT(*) AS total_events,
    COUNT(DISTINCT user_identity.email) AS distinct_users
  FROM access.audit a
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON a.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE a.event_date BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
  GROUP BY week_start
)
SELECT
  week_start,
  total_events,
  distinct_users,
  ROUND((total_events - LAG(total_events) OVER (ORDER BY week_start)) * 100.0 /
    NULLIF(LAG(total_events) OVER (ORDER BY week_start), 0), 1) AS events_growth_pct,
  ROUND((distinct_users - LAG(distinct_users) OVER (ORDER BY week_start)) * 100.0 /
    NULLIF(LAG(distinct_users) OVER (ORDER BY week_start), 0), 1) AS users_growth_pct
FROM weekly_stats
ORDER BY week_start

datasets.name: ae01d013
queryLines:
WITH workspace AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name,
    concat(COALESCE(workspace_name, ''), ' (id: ', workspace_id, ')') AS workspace_label
  FROM access.workspaces_latest
),
workspace_filtered AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name, workspace_label
  FROM workspace
  WHERE IF(:param_workspace = '<ALL WORKSPACES>', TRUE, workspace_label = :param_workspace)
),
job_stats AS (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_runs,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN result_state = 'SUCCESS' THEN 1 END) AS successful_runs
  FROM lakeflow.job_run_timeline j
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON j.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE CAST(j.period_start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
),
query_stats AS (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_queries,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN execution_status = 'FINISHED' THEN 1 END) AS successful_queries
  FROM query.history q
  INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON q.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
  WHERE CAST(q.start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
)
SELECT
  ROUND(j.successful_runs * 100.0 / NULLIF(j.total_runs, 0), 1) AS job_success_rate,
  ROUND(q.successful_queries * 100.0 / NULLIF(q.total_queries, 0), 1) AS query_success_rate,
  j.total_runs AS total_job_runs
FROM job_stats j CROSS JOIN query_stats q

datasets.name: ae01d016
queryLines:
WITH workspace AS (

SELECT
  COALESCE(jobs.name, CAST(j.job_id AS STRING)) AS job_name,
  j.job_id,
  COUNT(*) AS failure_count,
  MAX(CAST(j.period_start_time AS DATE)) AS last_failure_date
FROM lakeflow.job_run_timeline j
INNER JOIN workspace_filtered w ON j.workspace_id = w.workspace_id
LEFT JOIN lakeflow.jobs jobs ON j.job_id = jobs.job_id AND j.workspace_id = jobs.workspace_id
WHERE CAST(j.period_start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
  AND j.result_state IN ('FAILED', 'TIMEDOUT')
GROUP BY job_name, j.job_id
ORDER BY failure_count DESC
LIMIT 20

datasets.name: ae01d022
queryLines:
WITH workspace AS (
  SELECT workspace_id, workspace_name
  FROM access.workspaces_latest
),
user_counts AS (
  SELECT a.workspace_id,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN user_identity.email LIKE '%@%' THEN user_identity.email END) AS human_users,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN user_identity.email NOT LIKE '%@%' THEN user_identity.email END) AS service_principals,
    MAX(a.event_date) AS last_activity_date
  FROM access.audit a
  WHERE a.event_date BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
  GROUP BY a.workspace_id
),
query_counts AS (
  SELECT q.workspace_id, COUNT(*) AS total_queries
  FROM query.history q
  WHERE CAST(q.start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
  GROUP BY q.workspace_id
),
job_counts AS (
  SELECT j.workspace_id, COUNT(*) AS total_job_runs
  FROM lakeflow.job_run_timeline j
  WHERE CAST(j.period_start_time AS DATE) BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
  GROUP BY j.workspace_id
),
dbu_totals AS (
  SELECT u.workspace_id, ROUND(SUM(usage_quantity), 1) AS total_dbus
  FROM billing.usage u
  WHERE u.usage_date BETWEEN :param_date_range.min AND :param_date_range.max
  GROUP BY u.workspace_id
)
SELECT
  COALESCE(w.workspace_name, CAST(w.workspace_id AS STRING)) AS workspace_name,
  COALESCE(uc.human_users, 0) AS human_users,
  COALESCE(uc.service_principals, 0) AS service_principals,
  COALESCE(qc.total_queries, 0) AS total_queries,
  COALESCE(jc.total_job_runs, 0) AS total_job_runs,
  COALESCE(dt.total_dbus, 0) AS total_dbus,
  uc.last_activity_date
FROM workspace w
LEFT JOIN user_counts uc ON w.workspace_id = uc.workspace_id
LEFT JOIN query_counts qc ON w.workspace_id = qc.workspace_id
LEFT JOIN job_counts jc ON w.workspace_id = jc.workspace_id
LEFT JOIN dbu_totals dt ON w.workspace_id = dt.workspace_id
ORDER BY total_dbus DESC
